  "response": "Divya Bharti, a popular Bollywood actress of the early 1990s, died under mysterious circumstances on April 5, 1993, at the age of 19. Her death was controversial due to several factors:\n\n1. Sudden and unexplained fall: She reportedly fell from the fifth floor of her apartment in Mumbai, which raised suspicions about whether it was an accident or murder.\n\n2. Multiple theories: There were various speculations about her death, including:\n- Suicide\n- Accidental fall\n- Possible murder\n- Involvement of film industry connections\n\n3. Young age: She was at the peak of her career and her sudden death shocked the entire film industry.\n\n4. Personal life rumors: There were rumors about her personal relationships and alleged conflicts in her professional and personal life.\n\n5. Unclear circumstances: The exact details surrounding her death were never conclusively established, which led to continued speculation and conspiracy theories.\n\n6. High-profile status: As a popular actress with numerous film projects, her death attracted significant media attention and public interest.\n\nDespite multiple investigations, the precise cause of her death remains unresolved, which continues to make it a controversial topic in Bollywood history.",
